{"chapter_number":81,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":7,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"التكوير","name_complex":"At-Takwīr","name_simple":"At-Takwir","verses_count":29,"pages":[586,586],"meaning":{"text":"The Overthrowing","en":"The Overthrowing","id":"Menggulung"},"verses":[[[1,5801,"81:1","إِذَا الشَّمْسُ كُوِّرَتْ",["When the sun is covered,","Apabila matahari digulung,"],586,30,59,234,null,null],[2,5802,"81:2","وَإِذَا النُّجُومُ انكَدَرَتْ",["And when the stars darken,","dan apabila bintang-bintang berjatuhan,"],586,30,59,234,null,null],[3,5803,"81:3","وَإِذَا الْجِبَالُ سُيِّرَتْ",["And when the mountains are made to pass away,","dan apabila gunung-gunung dihancurkan,"],586,30,59,234,null,null],[4,5804,"81:4","وَإِذَا الْعِشَارُ عُطِّلَتْ",["And when the camels are left untended,","dan apabila unta-unta yang bunting ditinggalkan (tidak terurus),"],586,30,59,234,null,null],[5,5805,"81:5","وَإِذَا الْوُحُوشُ حُشِرَتْ",["And when the wild animals are made to go forth,","dan apabila binatang-binatang liar dikumpulkan,"],586,30,59,234,null,null],[6,5806,"81:6","وَإِذَا الْبِحَارُ سُجِّرَتْ",["And when the seas are set on fire,","dan apabila lautan dipanaskan,"],586,30,59,234,null,null],[7,5807,"81:7","وَإِذَا النُّفُوسُ زُوِّجَتْ",["And when souls are united,","dan apabila roh-roh dipertemukan (dengan tubuh),"],586,30,59,234,null,null],[8,5808,"81:8","وَإِذَا الْمَوْءُودَةُ سُئِلَتْ",["And when the female infant buried alive is asked","dan apabila bayi-bayi perempuan yang dikubur hidup-hidup ditanya,"],586,30,59,234,null,null],[9,5809,"81:9","بِأَيِّ ذَنبٍ قُتِلَتْ",["For what sin she was killed,","karena dosa apa dia dibunuh?"],586,30,59,234,null,null],[10,5810,"81:10","وَإِذَا الصُّحُفُ نُشِرَتْ",["And when the books are spread,","Dan apabila lembaran-lembaran (catatan amal) telah dibuka lebar-lebar,"],586,30,59,234,null,null],[11,5811,"81:11","وَإِذَا السَّمَاءُ كُشِطَتْ",["And when the heaven has its covering removed,","dan apabila langit dile